frameDefinitions: This frame concerns an Evaluee being judged for its quality, i.e. how much it would probably be liked.
An Entity is in motion  at a particular Speed, a momentaneous description of distance traveled per time.
A Person or Institution is being described in terms of their wealthiness, in other words the amount of money in their possession.
An Experiencer is involved in a bodily injury to a Body_part.
A Person is in a state of prosperity and/or renown after some period of development or hardship in an Endeavor.
An Entity is in a state such that it participates in a preponderance of states and events which are desirable for it.
frameExamples: I think that I <t>hurt</t> myself pretty bad back there.
In the 1920s the peach industry <t>flourished</t> in Upson County.
listRoleDefinitions: The <fen>Evaluee</fen> is being judged for its quality.
This role marks expressions that denote a scalar property of the <fen>Evaluee</fen> with respect to which the <fen>Evaluee</fen> is judged.
The <fen>Entity</fen> whose <fen>Speed</fen> is under consideration.

The feature of an <fen>Entity</fen> which is a function of the distance that the <fen>Entity</fen> moves in a given duration. With the adjectives of this frame this Frame Element is generally incorporated.
A quantity or other characterization of the <fen>Entity</fen>'s speed.
A modifier expressing  the deviation of the <fen>Speed</fen> from the norm.
The <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Entity</fen> is in the state of having  a particular <fen>Speed</fen>.
The individual or individuals whose wealthiness is being described.
A group which has (or lacks) possession of some resource.
The location on the body of the <fen>Experiencer</fen> where the bodily injury takes place.
The being or entity that is injured.
The time when the harming event occurs.
The place where the harming event occurs.
A sentient being or group of beings that is prosperous or well known after being involved in some <fen>Endeavor</fen>.
An event that the <fen>Person</fen> is involved in which leads to their state of prosperity or renown.
The time when the <fen>Entity</fen> is determined to be successful.
The <t>Entity</t> is experiencing a period of desirable events or states.
This role describes the state of the <fen>Entity</fen>. It is often incorporated into the LUs of this frame.
The <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Entity</fen> thrives.
The <fen>Place</fen> where the thriving takes place.
listRoleExamples: The Beaujolais Nouveau is dazzling <fex>in freshness</fex>.
<fex>Pat and Kim</fex> are completely broke at the moment.
I cut <fex>my finger</fex> on the envelope.
<fex>The squirrel</fex> abraded <fex>its</fex> tail as it twitched nervously in the confined space.
So you cut your leg on the window frame <fex>at six o'clock</fex>, correct?
She fell and hit her head <fex>out in the playground</fex>.
<fex>He</fex> became a success at the age of 25.
Looking back, I had a very successful <fex>career</fex>.
After 20 years of hard work, he finally made it as an artist <fex>in '84</fex>.
In the 1920s <fex>the peach industry</fex> thrived in Upson County.
He was living <fex>well</fex> after his promotion.
<fex>In the 1920s</fex> the peach industry thrived in Upson County.
Why was it that democracy flourished <fex>in America</fex>?
